&lt;h2 id=&#34;key-takeaways&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Takeaways:&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrating this keyboard into my setup is a financial investment in my productivity. Similar to hardware upgrades for a home lab, this purchase supports long-term personal development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;My setup includes both physical keyboard buttons and usage of the on-screen virtual stream deck interface. This dual-input approach optimizes task management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands down, best keyboard ever built!&lt;/li&gt;
